===[[Pokémon Masters EX]]===
{{main|Ghetsis (Masters)}}
Ghetsis, in his {{B2W2}} design, forms a [[sync pair]] with {{p|Kyurem}} in [[Pokémon Masters EX]]. Ghetsis became a playable sync pair on May 4, 2021.

In this game, Ghetsis was taken from an [[Pokémon multiverse|alternate universe]], as he was surprised when he learned that some characters such as {{mas|N}} already knew that Kyurem can {{pkmn|fusion|fuse}} with {{p|Reshiram}} and {{p|Zekrom}}, a fact that N learned from Ghetsis himself in Pokémon Black 2 and White 2. He has made notable appearances in the game's main stories: the [[Legendary Adventures]], and is the overall secondary antagonist of the [[villain arc]]. The whereabouts of Ghetsis from this game's continuity are currently unknown. 

